name: CheckiO PyCharm Edu plugin
body:
#  Welcome to CheckiO PyCharm Plugin
CheckiO PyCharm Plugin is plugin for [PyCharm Edu] (https://www.jetbrains.com/pycharm-edu/)  to solve missions from [CheckIO] (http://www.checkio.org/). 

## Features

### Special CheckIO project in PyCharm Edu 

### Available missions grouped by stations in Project view

### Mission text panel with action toolbar

### User info panel

### Solution checking

### Publications

### Hints
